result.name: Kamitora Tonkotsu

reviews.text: Why haven't I frequent this place before? I'm a big fan of dip ramen, and this place not only serves it, but it's delicious! Generous portions, too. It's the most expensive item on the menu, but reasonably prices. Great service. You can smell the variety of fragrances the moment you step in. And comfortable, spacious seating even at the kitchen counter. Their soup ramen is just as good!
Tasty Japanese Ramen  especially the soup.

Ramen is hard to rate because some of it is "5* reliably delicious and comforting", and others are "5*: a whole new realm of taste experience." I'd say this is part of the former group. A good ramen place in Wanchai to return to. Staff were very friendly and attentive, too. They are generous with the pork.

One of the better fast ramen I've visited in Hong Kong. While not "classic", the broth is rather mid and not very sadly, making it very feasible to also take a lot of the broth from the bowl. Great set of ramen round and a very decent price even though a premium is applied. Recommended if you like ramen and want a quick bite which doesn't raise your bid pressure.
Best Ramen in wanchai, for a very good Price 😋

result.name: 神虎麺商店

reviews.text: 欣賞佢哋無加一，加一係香港餐廳最無稽嘅慣例，好多自稱正宗/日本人開嘅日本餐廳都有收加一，我心入面係會對於呢d餐廳減分。講返食物質素，我唯一挑剔就係拉麵有鹼水味，其餘食材都食得出係用心之作。

Why haven't I frequent this place before? I'm a big fan of dip ramen, and this place not only serves it, but it's delicious! Generous portions, too. It's the most expensive item on the menu, but reasonably prices. Great service. You can smell the variety of fragrances the moment you step in. And comfortable, spacious seating even at the kitchen counter. Their soup ramen is just as good!

一試愛上😍神虎精選豚腩肉
餐廳地方都幾大，一張長抬面向拉麵師傅，靠牆同門口都有４人或多人坐位，位置寬敞舒服

食到主要有６款拉麵，但都係由元虎做Basic由豚骨精練而成
每款拉麵都可以＋＄３２轉做精選，會多左溏心蛋、豚腩肉、筍、紫菜
我就直接叫左神虎精選＄１１８
湯底都是豚骨湯，用上西班牙豬肉，灸燒過既豬腩肉，油脂豐富一層層咖，每一啖都好邪惡但濃郁既豬肉香真係會令人食上癮；
裡面仲有一片叉燒，食個油脂分佈均衡，唔鐘意食肥既人可以食叉燒
豬肉丸都係餐廳自家製，蓮藕加豬肉打制而成

海老虎＄９８
同樣係豚骨湯底再加左大量櫻花蝦 同 蝦味噌，湯底更加鮮味濃郁，麵質爽口輕易做到掛湯效果，啖啖都係精華

神虎餃子＄４２
餃子係餐廳每日朝早自家製作，比一般既餃子大隻，餡料都係豬肉

炸雞＄３８
依個炸雞真係超好食[色]超好食超好食[抓狂]講左3次就知真係好好食，無骨雞一咬d汁爆哂出黎，非常嫩滑既雞肉，一定會為左炸雞而再黎呀😃
拉麵好，炸雞滑。

終於食到啦（基本上係等佢開門，我排第一）✌🏻😁
特色蟹肉沾麵，200g 份量已經好夠
一句講哂：真係好掂👍🏻

要再來😄
